data.description: Welcome to your new home! Beautiful three bedroom, two full bathroom, two floors home with a large open living room. Close proximity to shopping and dining and everything nice that Arlington has to offer (Arlington Highlands, The Parks Mall, Grand Prairie Premium Outlets) Less than 5 minutes away from the main highways I20&360. The entrance greets you with a brick surround fireplace for the cold winters. Hardwood floors throughout the kitchen, living, and dining area. The dining area and additional breakfast area are plenty of room for the family gatherings. Granite counter tops and back splash in kitchen and both bathrooms. The master bedroom is on the first floor. Equipped with a washer and dryer room and utility room underneath the stairs for extra storage. Corner lot gives you plenty of space for beautiful landscape and a huge backyard. Covered porch and two car attached garage with double doors. Being sold AS-IS. Dont miss the opportunity and schedule your showing today!
